ModIdeas
========

/* TinkersCrafting */
//GEARS
- Create wood/stone gears same as usual
- Create metal gears by placing stone gear on casting bench and pooring Motlen <Ingot Name> on top of it. 
- 5 Ingots per Gear

//ARMOR
- Tinkers Armor
- Chest/Leg/Feet/Helm casts
- Bone Upgrades
- - Adds protection
- - 50 bones per protection level
- Magma Cream
- - Fire Resistance
- - 10 magma cream per protection level
- Cactus
- - Damage opponent when you are hit with melee (10% chance at level 1, 30% chance at level 3)
- - 50 cactus per level
- Redstone (legs only)
- - Run speed
- - 50 redstone is +2% run speed (max 3 levels)
- Lapis
- - Chance to parry/dodge
- Emerald
- - Durability bonus
- Diamond
- - Durability bonus
- Wither Bone
- - Regen
- -- 1/2 heart per 30 seconds
- -- 10 seconds time reduction per level (max level 3)
- --- I.E. 1/2 every 20 seconds at level 2, 10 seconds at level 3
- 
